			<attribute id="nextNodeId" type="uint32" value="7" />
			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="Dialogue with the ghost of Sendai, bound to eternal service to Bhaal in her afterlife. In &quot;Baldur's Gate 2: Throne of Bhaal&quot;, Sendai was one of the Five, an evil group of Bhaalspawn led by Amelyssan." />
